/*********************************************************
	this demo is a ping process.
----------------------------------------------------------
function:
	echo:
		user send a string (123456) to kernel
	
		kernel reply string (1234567) to user
	print:
		user send string (Hello World !) to kernel
	
		kernel reply unsigned int (1) to user
additional:
	user program build using libnl

architecture:
	Kernel modules and user programs have the same header files for easy modification

**********************************************************/
